= Action name = PCK.AUTOMIC_SONIC.PUB.ACTION.RUN_SONIC_COMMAND
= General description = This action will execute a command on sonic.
=Setup= * For SSH, Enable SSH on the target system.
= Inputs = - Command* : Provide command to be executed
= Failure Conditions = If the user provides invalid command. If user will not provide sudo credentials properly.
=Return Value= &UC4RB_SONIC_OUTPUT# AE variable containing output result of command execution
= Logging = Logs will be displayed in the AE report.
= Example = * Command : show clock ----------------------------------------------
